{
	"VersionNumber": 4,
	"ResourceName": "auth0_eventTypes",
	"Description": "This is intended to be used as a lookup file providing additional information regarding Auth0 event types. It is used within the Auth0 Kit for dashboards, macros, scheduled searches, alerts, flows, and templates.\n\nFields:\ncategory,subcategory,eventType,description,is_mod\n  - category: this is the category of the eventType.\n  - subcategory: this is the subcategory within the category for the eventType.\n  - eventType: this is the eventType you will find at the references below and within your logs.\n  - description: this will give you more information about the eventType.\n  - is_mod: this field displays whether the field is a known modification eventType\n\nReference(s):\n  - Auth0 \n    - https://auth0.com/docs/deploy-monitor/logs/log-event-type-codes\n\nUsage: lookup -r eventType eventType (category subcategory description)\ndump -r auth0_eventTypes | table",
	"Labels": [
		"auth0"
	],
